comments: Lopez (MIL) moves alongside Davis' (LAL) path and the contact during the shot attempt is marginal.
Walker IV (LAL) and Middleton (MIL) mutually engage and disengage as Middleton is running through the lane.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) briefly rests his arm on Walker IV's (LAL) side during the pick.
Walker IV (LAL) absorbs the contact initiated by Middleton (MIL) and maintains a legal guarding position during the shot attempt.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) is in the paint for longer than three seconds without actively guarding an opponent.
Middleton (MIL) and Westbrook (LAL) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Middleton (MIL) and Westbrook (LAL) come together and marginal contact occurs as both players dive on the floor for the loose ball.
James (LAL) slightly extends his arm into Antetokounmpo (MIL) at the end of his drive toward the rim.
As James (LAL) recovers the loose ball and is already off-balance, Middleton (MIL) reaches in and any contact is marginal.
Davis (LAL) is set in Holiday's (MIL) path and marginal contact occurs as Holiday is moving over the top of the pick.
Westbrook (LAL) and Antetokounmpo (MIL) mutually engage and disengage during the rebound attempt.
Beverley's (LAL) hand slides off of Middleton's (MIL) side and marginal contact occurs during the inbound.
Middleton (MIL) commits a take foul on Westbrook (LAL). The transition take foul rule does not apply to the last two minutes of either the fourth quarter or overtime.
Antetokounmpo (MIL) commits a take foul on Davis (LAL).
